"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 348px; height: 288px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Sagittal fast spin-echo T2-weighted MR image obtained before embolization shows global uterine enlargement and diffuse adenomyosis. Junctional zone thickness (arrow) is 14 mm.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"    </div>",
"   </div>",
"  </div>",
" </div>",
