"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Sagittal spin-echo T2-weighted MR image",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 357px; height: 365px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Sagittal spin-echo T2-weighted MR image obtained three months after embolization shows normal junctional zone thickness (arrow). The patient's symptoms improved significantly after uterine fibroid embolization. Follow-up MR of the pelvis one year later showed no changes from 3-month follow-up study and no evidence of recurrence.",
