"       <td colspan=\"2\">",
"        Abnormal",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"     </tbody>",
"    </table>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The unscored portion of the Standardized Assessment of Concussion (SAC) includes a graded symptom checklist, a brief neurologic examination, and records the presence of post-traumatic and retrograde amnesia.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
